---
import StaticLayout from '../layouts/StaticLayout.astro';
---

<StaticLayout title="About FreeToolStack" description="Learn about FreeToolStack - free online tools that respect your privacy.">
  <p>
    FreeToolStack is a collection of free online tools designed with one principle in mind:
    <strong>your privacy matters</strong>.
  </p>

  <h2>How It Works</h2>
  <p>
    Every tool on FreeToolStack runs entirely in your browser using modern web technologies.
    When you upload a file or enter text, the processing happens on your device — nothing is
    sent to our servers. This means your data stays private, and the tools work even without
    an internet connection (once loaded).
  </p>

  <h2>Why We Built This</h2>
  <p>
    We were tired of "free" tools that require signups, upload your files to unknown servers,
    and plaster your screen with ads. FreeToolStack is different: genuinely free, genuinely private,
    and genuinely useful.
  </p>

  <h2>Technology</h2>
  <p>
    Our tools are built with modern web standards including WebAssembly (WASM), the Web Crypto API,
    Canvas API, and other browser-native technologies. This allows us to offer professional-grade
    tools without any server-side processing.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    Have a suggestion for a new tool? Found a bug? We'd love to hear from you.
    Visit our <a href="/contact">contact page</a> to get in touch.
  </p>
</StaticLayout>
